    "description": "&quot;<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/89d045898aedeee19cc948ad94ca87a0.avif?t=1680537940\" width=610 height=244 /></span><br> 从圣拉斐尔北部街角一个小店开始，人称“带头老爸”的劳尔和他的妻子格洛丽亚一起，建立了一个充斥着鲜血和子弹的帝国，当然，偶尔也会经营一些小菜。<br> <br> “副官包 - 家族”DLC解锁一套5个副官，他们具有独特的能力，将辅助你开展征服。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/d725bd8c1c95d722ca3481b2bcd9b69f.avif?t=1680537940\" width=545 height=108 /></span><br> <strong>劳尔·瑞斯</strong> - “带头老爸”本人，他是制造、销售和使用各种武器的专家，当然，他首先是一位家族头领。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/57af1e29e900b3f702f7d474fcb9d391.webp?t=1680537940\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>家族之锤</strong><br> 当他与家族并肩战斗时，力量临时增加4。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/085ceb657d68f2be4ace84a3cf6c5f29.webp?t=1680537940\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>家族生意</strong><br> 与这个角色达成协议可获得各种益处。当卡特尔拥有所有家族成员时即可使用。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/42a68d326650341b683ae6401ad70077.avif?t=1680537940\" width=545 height=123 /></span><br> <strong>格洛丽亚·瑞斯</strong> - 母亲兼管理者，她能让你的企业生产、包装和运送更多的商品，获得更多利润。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/2fc725145fea9a574f6c0a40613d089b.webp?t=1680537940\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>家族保护者</strong><br> 如果有家族成员参与战斗，母亲可以干扰警察、联邦警察和缉毒局的攻击。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/cefaefefc32dad0648af179c50705002.avif?t=1680537940\" width=545 height=122 /></span><br> <strong>凯蒂·瑞斯</strong> - 瑞斯家族最小的成员，她能增加武器在销售点的价格，并且能在战场上为自己的家族成员壮胆。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/c6498da5219e7ee08947adc003a37581.webp?t=1680537940\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>家族灵魂</strong><br> 在对战中，增加所有家族成员的力量。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/35d5e20fd28e9a8defe54a9db1619d5a.webp?t=1680537940\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>武器贩子</strong><br> 在有副官驻扎的地方，可以影响边境上的武器销售价格，令价格增加5%<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/ee2d5a9249b875373127143ce2c0db19.webp?t=1680537940\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>胆小鬼</strong><br> 当副官耐力下降太多时，可以逃离对战。如果老大哥马克也参与了对战，则这项能力失效。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/c993ee1c4eadd55bff2392e8fb636cec.avif?t=1680537940\" width=545 height=122 /></span><br> <strong>马克·瑞斯</strong> - 马克是长子兼瑞斯王朝的继承人，他天生具有雄心壮志，因此在战斗时格外勇猛。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/525f2183c50ab6d0642c64f3d7ce2bee.webp?t=1680537940\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>妹妹的照护</strong><br> 鼓舞人心的妹妹凯蒂。她不会逃离战场。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/b74e66c866b52796cf9cbeb17756a2de.avif?t=1680537940\" width=547 height=121 /></span><br> <strong>加斯帕·瑞斯</strong> - 加斯帕是驾驶专家，能将货物运送到任何需要的地方，但也会令他的哥哥绞尽脑汁……当然，是为了家族的利益。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/5a5ea693f6c2daf425008fd821feed46.webp?t=1680537940\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>激发老大哥</strong><br> 如果弟弟加斯帕与老大哥马克一起战斗，马可可以使用自己的辅助攻击而无需冷却。<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316200/extras/35d5e20fd28e9a8defe54a9db1619d5a.webp?t=1680537940\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>达成交易：武器</strong><br> 选择“达成交易”特殊指令。交易达成后，你将可以更好的价格出售某项产品。&quot;",
